{"tid":1919234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"壯陽村隔離人士正仆街","createTime":"2020-03-10T15:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T06:45:06.000Z","uid":133159,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f067e47de6da87a9ea677fb6930d03f09f5346fd","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，<br />\n你班仆街當自己大爺，<br />\n人屌夜屌，你老母你公主號班仆街，<br />\n個個都有公主病，自己行李又要人幫你搬，<br />\n你真喺當呢度喺郵輪啊？<br />\n你哋隔離14日啊，仆你個臭街未夠鐘就話要走，唔畀走又屌，你估我哋好想留住你哋啊？<br />\n個個走嗰時都一箱兩箱，梗係啦一日要8個杯麵，一日要一枝洗髮露，沐浴露，畀你都仲要過隔離偷，偷日用品都算，仆你個臭街仲要偷你鄰居啲飯，你偷撚咗人哋食乜春啊<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e0d860674637fc1afe6d49c70226011cf6179f","tid":1919234,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"樓主好大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c7dcde588b5031e4ad8b25c9a99393dd3e3be0","tid":1919234,"uid":334523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"人性醜惡<br />\n人嘅教育水平唔好咪咁樣"},{"pid":"2cc10f0cebc36359f3e0d0e63e0404a7f8b34688","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"再講吓武漢班PK<br />\n政府免費包機送你班仆街返嚟，你咪算執到<br />\n又要返嚟，又要唔想入壯陽村，仆你個街日日喺到屌又投訴又自殺又盛，唔通畀你班仆街周街行播毒啊？又多要求，又喺瘋狂攞物資，攞完又攞，日日都攞淋浴露，唔講以為你哋一日沖十次涼，最變態喺有條仆街每隔兩個鐘攞一次消毒用品，攞去飲啊？<br />\n<br />\n最難頂有個精神病患者，每日定時定候落嚟狂屌，打老婆打到入醫院，遲早有一日發作<br />\n<br />\n你班武漢港人，有幾多喺真。香港人，大部份都喺講普通話，我接電話十次有八次都要講蝗語，政府啲錢就使撚晒落班仆街到<br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01260d4040a59cacd6ac2d31a6e1da65daa68d45","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"30c7dcde588b5031e4ad8b25c9a99393dd3e3be0","tid":1919234,"uid":334523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"人性醜惡<br />\n人嘅教育水平唔好咪咁樣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"但你起碼唔好偷撚咗人哋個飯啊，偷撚咗食乜啊"},{"pid":"2a0d2cd8e152a98dc8b5bc0fe142e92e3c4a3cf4","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d3f8d3b0dfbaa1bb9738287c7573a3edd28416ce","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4db6fc4f95cc93b3419872d5a6f77bd0d3b580bc","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"63432d3bc49475918e981e2af37599bcf3a02213","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a6c00d068df26cf1586157de34f2e29fdb2f1d0f","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b26fc29c453e3e0219518335e7bbab16ec516aeb","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"86b5fe100eb1663d8ffc0d132b816a617ccba0f2","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"5a8bac2c7d6ddc0f006db8b18258ffbca143a9ad","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"1bfe716d0c55d8ed8f062795b0bc2ae533aa16c8","tid":1919234,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"601c23376be355214cc734186a8ad51ea0d